Dim TagArea As Integer Dim TagPrioridade As Integer Dim TagSelecionaTopo As Boolean Dim NumEvents, NumEvents_old As Integer
Private Sub Display_AnimationStart()
'Verifica erro On Error GoTo ErrHandler
TagArea = 0 TagPrioridade = 0 TagSelecionaTopo = True
'Sai da sub-rotina Exit Sub ErrHandler:
'Registra o erro LogDiagnosticsMessage "VBA Error (Display_AnimationStart()): " & Hex(Err.Number) & " - " & Err.Description, ftDiagSeverityError
End Sub

Private Sub BtAreaTodos_Released()
On Error GoTo ErrHandler

Select Case TagPrioridade Case 0 ExecuteCommand ("Invoke Me.AlarmEventSummary1.FilterName(AreaTodos)") Case 1 ExecuteCommand ("Invoke Me.AlarmEventSummary1.FilterName(AreaTodosTodos)") Case 2 ExecuteCommand ("Invoke Me.AlarmEventSummary1.FilterName(AreaTodosAlta)") Case 3 ExecuteCommand ("Invoke Me.AlarmEventSummary1.FilterName(AreaTodosMedia)") Case 4 ExecuteCommand ("Invoke Me.AlarmEventSummary1.FilterName(AreaTodosBaixa)") End Select

End Sub
